result.name: The Spaghetti House

reviews.text:
Parts of the airport is under construction so it was a little hard to find the place. It's well worth it though as the food is excellent. The pizza and pasta are top-notch and the Chicken Caesar salad made for a great starter. The service was quite good as well.

The only problem is having to go all the way outside of the restaurant to wash your hands or go to the bathroom.

The dishes were very nice, all of them especially what we ordered lasagna deluxe and spaghetti bolognese, and the feee flow water helps too as we like to drink water very much. The only thing probably was the price which quite high and no promotion
Best spaghetti carbonara I've had

Food is okay, but simply not enough staff in the morning. The waitress tried her very best, but run off her feet seating, serving, cleaning and taking food out, so some of the food was stone cold once it arrived.

1st of all, the food was less than average....I paid approximately $120.00 CAD currency, for a plain, no flavour meal....my 2 dependent sons and I did not enjoy the meal....when it came time to pay....I used my credit card....the old girl that was taking the payment kept attempting to grab my credit card out of my hand....I did not allow her to grab my credit card....she became enraged, and stormed off....a younger man took my payment, with no attitude....I informed him that she should learn to control her emotions....she has no right to demand to hold my credit card....there is no need for anyone to ever touch my belongings....I can put the card in myself, and type the pin in myself

result.name: The Spaghetti House

reviews.text:
Parts of the airport is under construction so it was a little hard to find the place. It's well worth it though as the food is excellent. The pizza and pasta are top-notch and the Chicken Caesar salad made for a great starter. The service was quite good as well.

The only problem is having to go all the way outside of the restaurant to wash your hands or go to the bathroom.

Very very bad service when the stuff lead the table. She made us feel like inferior guest. The phone of customer service also very unfriendly. Made 2 phone call with nobody answered.

餐廳帶位小姐看到我們一家帶小孩子就不允許我們坐在窗戶旁邊(可以讓小朋友看到飛機)而是她指定的位子，窗戶旁的位子並沒有標明關閉，而是她說明是晚一點才會開放，可能12點以後吧？(她自己的語調是疑問句)可是當時中午已經11：55了，其實非常不舒服的感覺有被歧視，不懂一間餐廳的訓練怎麼能訓練出一個這樣有歧視話術的服務生出來？
這件餐廳的客服電話也沒人接，打了兩次還留言，沒人有回應，如果可以不給星甚至負評我一定給負的分數。

J'ai commandé des Spaghetti 2 fromages aux crabe et crevettes, au final Aucun fromage dans mes pâtes mais plein de crème. Pâtes pas assez cuites. Crevettes surgelées. Et pas de crabe. Aucune saveur. Aucun intérêt. Rien d'italien dans ce plat.

The dishes were very nice, all of them especially what we ordered lasagna deluxe and spaghetti bolognese, and the feee flow water helps too as we like to drink water very much. The only thing probably was the price which quite high and no promotion

On a un petit-déjeuner (brunch). Rien d'exceptionnel... Plutôt fade.
Il y a des formules brunch avec de la quantité. Mais question qualité ce n'est pas ça...
